---
title: Quick Double Bacon & Green Bean Fried Rice  with Fried Egg & Coriander
description: Put down that takeaway menu and hang up the phone because we have a fuss-free fried rice that you’re going to love! Fluffy rice is finished off in a frying pan with an array of colourful veggies, soy flavours, and golden diced bacon. Top it off with a sunny fried egg and you’ll never need takeaway again.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6617a1d6300be64307bdf78d-bbb6c458.jpeg
